   <talk_paragraph index="n024_adventurer_guildmaster_decud-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n024_adventurer_guildmaster_decud-1-b" mid="16" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>So, why are you still asking me to do all kinds of things?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer's Guild Master Deckard$<BR>No, I feel strange. You look so gentle and weak when you first come to Calderock Village. I doubt you can hold it for long.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n024_adventurer_guildmaster_decud-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n024_adventurer_guildmaster_decud-1-c" mid="18" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>So, you are just crapping.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer's Guild Master Deckard$<BR>That's because, if I said you can't make it from the start, you will be disappointed, isn't it? Moreover, you have recommendation letter, so, I was thinking of encouraging you first.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n024_adventurer_guildmaster_decud-1-c" image="QN_Master_Decud.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n024_adventurer_guildmaster_decud-1-d" mid="20" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>You are betting with others on this matter?!</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer's Guild Master Deckard$<BR>Hahaha, not exactly that.<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Deckard tries hard to get that over)</FONT><BR>So, I bet with the others that you will run off fast.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n024_adventurer_guildmaster_decud-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n024_adventurer_guildmaster_decud-1-e" mid="22" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(......)</html>]]></talk_answer>
