   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n024_adventurer_guildmaster_decud-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n024_adventurer_guildmaster_decud-1-f" mid="24" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(If that's the case, why said all these...)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer's Guild Master Deckard$<BR>Keke, why are you so serious?<BR>I asked for you today,<BR>not because I have lost <FONT color=#a82424>half of my assets</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n024_adventurer_guildmaster_decud-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n024_adventurer_guildmaster_decud-1-g" mid="26" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Yes, I understand.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer's Guild Master Deckard$<BR>Hope everything will be <FONT color=#a82424>smooth</FONT> for you in the future.<BR>This is definitely not because I had used <FONT color=#a82424>The other half of my assets</FONT> to bet that you will have a great success. You understand what I mean?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n024_adventurer_guildmaster_decud-1-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n024_adventurer_guildmaster_decud-1-h" mid="29" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Ok, whatever you say.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="28"><![CDATA[<html>$Adventurer's Guild Master Deckard$<BR>Hope you can work hard for the world's love and peace!<BR>If I lost this time again, I would literally <FONT color=#a82424>lost everything</FONT>. Understand?<BR>I didn't say these because I'm afraid of bankruptcy.</html>]]></talk_question>
